name: OMEGA - TRUST (Operation Mission & Economical Growth Association Trust)

briefDescription: Our NGO Omega - Operation Mission and Economical Growth Association has established in 2013 at Manamadurai, Sivaganga Dist. Tamil Nadu, S.India. With the great vision for the development of down trodden, political, social, economically challenged people with education and empowerment of various areas especially for the children and poor students. Our main motto of NGO is to innovate in rural development, political, social and economical areas in future.  Socially our main aspect of work is to integrate and attach the Government and Non-Governmental organization for development of our parliament constituency of Sivagangai District in Tamil Nadu.
